snippet.title: [Nintendo 64DD] Kyojin no Doshin 2 Gameplay (2)
snippet.description: http://64DD.net Another video showing the gameplay, but with a different pavillon, different Queen Companion. It especially differs in the way that I on purpose failed the mission the Queen asked me to do. She's very upset...
